{"TopicId":111158,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Ask the Mods questions about the Forums!","CreatedByName":"Dman979","CreatedById":123837,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-28T17:01:51Z","PageNum":269,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-06-17T00:30:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#1b1e1f;color:#c9c5be;font-size:15px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003EWhat is forum moderation to you personally\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is a hobby for me. My interest in the game itself waxes and wanes over time, but I\u0027ve made a great set of friends here.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#1b1e1f;color:#c9c5be;font-size:15px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003EHow do you folks organize things with other moderators behind the scenes\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe have an internal chat where we discuss moderation. But mostly make stupid jokes.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#1b1e1f;color:#c9c5be;font-size:15px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003EWhat are some difficult choices\u003Cspan\u003E\u00A0\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat to allow and what not to allow. One time I recall we discussed something for several hours before reluctantly saying we should risk letting it be posted. And not a single forum member ever commented on it.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#1b1e1f;color:#c9c5be;font-size:15px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003EWhat are some of the most fun and enjoyable activities you do as a moderator?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTalking to the guys.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#1b1e1f;color:#c9c5be;font-size:15px;text-align:left;\u0022\u003EHow much time in your day is taken up by moderation?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n30 minutes to 3 hours, depending on how busy things are.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rutabaga22","CreatedById":221143,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-06-17T17:56:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow does moderating actually work? Do you go through the posts you want to visit or do you skim through as many posts as possible looking for rule infractions or something else entirely?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-06-17T22:11:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI skip around and read threads which are interesting to me or which seem likely to experience trouble, and of course we look at the posts which are reported to us. Sometimes I just click on threads I don\u0027t normally read as a random check.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-06-18T11:07:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224294018\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221687024586\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022221143\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rutabaga22\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n17 hours ago, Rutabaga22 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow does moderating actually work? Do you go through the posts you want to visit or do you skim through as many posts as possible looking for rule infractions or something else entirely?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI do not think of myself as a forum police officer looking for some unsuspecting forum speeder to give a ticket to, if that\u0027s what you\u0027re wondering. I simply go do what I like to do on the forum. I participate in the forum games, I share my screenshots, I welcome newcomers to the forum and the game, and I do try to write my fan-fic. I also approve new member\u0027s posts, which I love doing. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EUnfortunately, I do have to put on the ol\u0027 moderator\u0027s hat when I come across stuff that shouldn\u0027t be here. But it\u0027s not for the reason some people think moderators do that kind of thing. We do it because the community deserves a place that\u0027s relatively free from disrespect and disruption. We have a reputation of being accepting and accommodating. We\u0027re a giant hug-box and have community members of all backgrounds, demographics, and every other box people come in (and I really hate boxes \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:huh:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_undecided.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:huh:\u0022\u003E people are people).\u00A0 And when someone disrupts that harmony, we have to do what we can to fix it. It\u0027s why we rely on the goodwill of the community to report what you come across so we can take care of those things. \u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"dsplaisted","CreatedById":225798,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-06-18T13:21:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy does the \u0022Do not click this\u0022 thread keep getting locked and unlocked?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starhawk","CreatedById":131400,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-06-18T13:44:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224294205\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221687094519\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022225798\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022dsplaisted\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 minutes ago, dsplaisted said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy does the \u0022Do not click this\u0022 thread keep getting locked and unlocked?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBecause it\u0027s a game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\nHappy landings!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-06-18T15:48:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224294205\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221687094519\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022225798\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022dsplaisted\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, dsplaisted said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy does the \u0022Do not click this\u0022 thread keep getting locked and unlocked?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u2019t think it\u2019s ever been unlocked.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kspbutitscursed","CreatedById":227529,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-06-18T23:42:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224294237\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221687103314\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 hours ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u2019t think it\u2019s ever been unlocked.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ni agree i has never EVER been unlocked since 2013\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superluminal Gremlin","CreatedById":221533,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-06-21T20:49:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat is the Longest Thread?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-06-21T21:21:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m not a Mod but I don\u0027t think anything rivals that\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002257228\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed5106653967\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/topic/27292-what-did-you-do-in-ksp1-today/?do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:377px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-06-22T13:08:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProbably right \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/150811-the-aziz/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022150811\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/150811-the-aziz/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@The Aziz\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-02T13:12:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere was a question about ignoring users but.. could there be an option to ignore threads? If I don\u0027t want to participate in one or something (I frequently visit forum sections, check if there are new posts and leave if there aren\u0027t any), I\u0027d simply mark one as ignored and it would be kept as read, without bolding when a new post appears.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe polar opposite of \u0022follow thread\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-07-02T13:12:55Z\u0022 title=\u002207/02/2023 01:12  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 2, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by The Aziz\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-02T15:48:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224299279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221688303548\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere was a question about ignoring users but.. could there be an option to ignore threads? If I don\u0027t want to participate in one or something (I frequently visit forum sections, check if there are new posts and leave if there aren\u0027t any), I\u0027d simply mark one as ignored and it would be kept as read, without bolding when a new post appears.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe polar opposite of \u0022follow thread\u0022.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhile an interesting idea, unlike a user who will just pop up randomly in threads you\u2019re reading, you could just not click on that thread? \u00A0 \u00A0I do see it\u2019s potential use though. \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-02T17:31:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSure, but when it\u0027s bolded it sort of \u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#003366;\u0022\u003E\u2022\u003C/span\u003E \u003C/strong\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#003366;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003Egrabs the attention\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E. \u0022Oh, is this something I\u0027ve not read yet?\u0022 And it turns out it\u0027s once again one of those threads I\u0027m not interested in reading. When ignored, it would simply fade into \u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#003366;\u0022\u003Ethe background of read/inactive threads.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-07-02T17:32:37Z\u0022 title=\u002207/02/2023 05:32  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 2, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by The Aziz\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-07T07:45:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThread1\u003Cbr\u003E\n[x]\u00A0 Always mark as being read.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(Just an idea)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"user544","CreatedById":224325,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-12T02:55:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhow to insert images onto replys and threads?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-12T04:14:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224301746\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221689130501\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022224325\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022user544\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, user544 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhow to insert images onto replys and threads?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHowdy. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0You should be able to simply copy a link into your post. You will need to put the image on a hosting site first, though. Imgur is easy to use and does not charge.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-12T06:13:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis not a question but I\u0027m happy to report that the forum doesn\u0027t lag anymore after removing the broken twitter widget. Looks like, as I suspected, it was the cause of the lag.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"user544","CreatedById":224325,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-13T02:22:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224301760\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221689135258\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 hours ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHowdy. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0You should be able to simply copy a link into your post. You will need to put the image on a hosting site first, though. Imgur is easy to use and does not charge.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBUT IT doas not work bruh\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-13T02:26:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224302004\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221689214955\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022224325\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022user544\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, user544 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBUT IT doas not work bruh\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt does work.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 Just paste a link directly to the image on the hosting service, not a website or a gallery. and it will embed.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 Something like www.imgur.com/blahblah/7dhj398fj390.png will embed directly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-13T05:15:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\ntesting\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022t3yHHuO.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.34\u0022 height=\u0022668\u0022 width=\u00221007\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/t3yHHuO.png\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-17T00:49:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224302021\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221689225340\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/13/2023 at 1:15 AM, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ntesting\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca data-fileid=\u0022undefined\u0022 href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/t3yHHuO.png\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022t3yHHuO.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.34\u0022 height=\u0022668\u0022 width=\u00221007\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/t3yHHuO.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027re better off using the one that says Direct link.\u00A0 I believe the Forums strip the \u003Cspan\u003E\u003C/span\u003E tag from the link, so the bbcode should work, but might not always work.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAziz, Light!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-17T02:39:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDirect is supposed to work better in chats while BBCode is for forums. Is what they say, anyway.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-17T06:08:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224303293\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221689554946\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAziz, Light!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022azizlight-fifthelement.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u0022100.00\u0022 height=\u0022220\u0022 width=\u0022220\u0022 src=\u0022https://media.tenor.com/s-uSZdI7kAgAAAAM/azizlight-fifthelement.gif\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JoeSchmuckatelli","CreatedById":154477,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-07-17T13:56:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m getting \u0027500\u0027 errors (forum can\u0027t handle the request) trying to link directly to Science and Spaceflight from a Google search.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Col\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nSearch: KSP Forums.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nClick \u0022Science \u0026amp; Spaceflight\u0022\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nfail\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ol\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt is intermittent.\u00A0 Happens both on mobile (Chrome) and PC (Edge).\u00A0 Always the same error.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#e67e22;\u0022\u003EAbove this line is a current problem being reported to the team\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#2980b9;\u0022\u003EWHY CAN I NOT SEPARATE THOUGHTS INTO DIFFERENT REPLIES?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#e67e22;\u0022\u003EBelow this line is a response to someone else\u0027s problem\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224301746\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221689130501\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022224325\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022user544\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/11/2023 at 10:55 PM, user544 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhow to insert images onto replys and threads?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224302004\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221689214955\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022224325\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022user544\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/12/2023 at 10:22 PM, user544 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBUT IT doas not work bruh\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224302005\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022111158\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221689215173\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/12/2023 at 10:26 PM, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt does work.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 Just paste a link directly to the image on the hosting service, not a website or a gallery. and it will embed.\u00A0\u00A0\u00A0 Something like www.imgur.com/blahblah/7dhj398fj390.png will embed directly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have to do an \u0027indirect\u0027 link from Imgur.\u00A0 Basically I upload the image to Imgur, then I skip trying to use the suggested link, right click on the image and open in new tab.\u00A0 That has an address that ends in something the forums will recognize.\u00A0 Copy and Paste and the image appears.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00224WnkiSb.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002291.50\u0022 height=\u0022724\u0022 width=\u00221200\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/4WnkiSb.jpg\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf I use the suggested link, all that shows up is the link - not the image\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://imgur.com/a/YoOnApG\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://imgur.com/a/YoOnApG\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#e67e22;\u0022\u003E...Okay, I used my current problem to highlight my answer to the other poster\u0027s problem.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-07-17T14:19:08Z\u0022 title=\u002207/17/2023 02:19  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Jul 17\u0022\u003EJuly 17, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by JoeSchmuckatelli\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}